# Join <%= @current_studio.name %>

<% if @current_user_is_member %>
You are already a member of this studio.

[Go to studio homepage](<%= @current_studio.path %>)
<% elsif @invite %>
You have been invited to join this studio.

## [Actions](<%= @current_studio.path %>/join/actions)

* [`join_studio()`](<%= @current_studio.path %>/join/actions/join_studio) to accept the invitation and join the studio.
<% elsif @current_studio.is_scene? %>
This is a scene (open studio). You can join directly.

## [Actions](<%= @current_studio.path %>/join/actions)

* [`join_studio()`](<%= @current_studio.path %>/join/actions/join_studio) to join the scene.
<% else %>
You need an invite code to join this studio.

## [Actions](<%= @current_studio.path %>/join/actions)

* [`join_studio(code)`](<%= @current_studio.path %>/join/actions/join_studio) to join with an invite code.
<% end %>
